<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.8.9">
<l>tañcami varkkeṉva ḷaiyunillā neñcamun tammatē cintittēṟku</l>
<l>vañcima ruṅkuṉe ruṅkanōkki vāytiṟan toṉṟupa ṇittatuṇṭu</l>
<l>nañcamu ṭaittivar nōkkunōkkam nāṉivar tammaiya ṟiyamāṭṭē</l>
<l>ṉañcuvaṉ maṟṟiva rārkkoleṉṉa vaṭṭapu yakarat tēṉeṉṟārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My bangles will not stay, [going] to him [for] refuge; for me</l>
<l rend="indent">who thinks [of him], my heart, too, is his.</l>
<l>Glancing so that my creeper[-thin] waist [felt] pressed, opening [his] mouth,</l>
<l rend="indent">there was one thing stated.</l>
<l>He glanced a glance afflicting [me like] poison.</l>
<l rend="indent">I am not able to understand him!</l>
<l>Besides, I am frightened! When I asked, “Who is this?”</l>
<l rend="indent">he answered, “I am he in the house of the eight-armed [lord].”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
